<br>
I find in outdoor zones it isn't needed. In indoor zones I like the hectic feel of not being able to stop a runner but typically kill things too fast to worry about it. As it is now I have crawled most of Crystal Caverns, TOFS, Nurga, Sol A and B, Najena, and many other dungeons solo for experience. It works better as at least a duo but it is possible. Crystal Caverns and TOFS really rock too.<br>
<br>
The deal with crawling dungeons is to go slow and make sure you kill anything in your way that you may bring aggro from.<br>
